name: Alex'sCoolProgram
0:
”Alexa, ask my cool program to tell me how cool I am.”
”Alexa, tell my cool program I am cool.”
”Alexa, ask my cool program to tell me how amazing I am.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my cool program
des:
This skill tells you how awesome and cool you are! Simply say one of the phrases below and Alexa will compliment you in return. That's it!
Phrases:
Tell me how cool I am.
I am cool.
I am amazing.
Tell me how amazing I am.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
